parameters: \n<Blonde>Like I can be bothered to help with the reconstruction work.

\n<Blonde>It's nice to go wild with the sexaroids, but man, they're so
inorganic and boring in personality.

\n<Blonde>\C[27]New model sexaroids\C[0]... coming to this town?! And
next week?!?

\n<Blonde>Quality like you're fucking a real human?! Even better than
fucking a real person they say?!?

\n<Blonde>Damn, I've found the joy of living. Hurry up and come to me,
new model sexaroid-chan!

\n<Eury>It's been \v[224] days since I arrived in Tengatsu City.
Let's do our best today too!
